            <title>[SOLR-3087] XInclude not working on schema.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-3087</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I want to use XML XInclude mechanism (&lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XInclude&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/XInclude&lt;/a&gt;) to include parts of schema.xml.&lt;br/&gt;
When I try to include a fieldType, I get this exception :&lt;/p&gt;

